text: Xingjing may refer to: *Xingjing, Ningxia (兴泾), a town in Xixia District, Yinchuan, Ningxia Hui Autonomous Region, China *Hetu Ala, the capital of Later Jin (1616–1636), also known as Xingjing (興京) after 1636, located in Xinbin Manchu Autonomous County, Liaoning, China *Gun Metal Grey (刑警), a 2010 Hong Kong TV series ==See also== *Xinjing (disambiguation)
title: Xingjing
